(define/contract (special-perm nums)
  (-> (listof exact-integer?) exact-integer?)
  
  (define mod-val 1000000007)

  (define (gcd a b)
    (if (= b 0) a (gcd b (modulo a b))))

  (define (lcm a b)
    (/ (* a b) (gcd a b)))

  (define (can-place? a b)
    (or (= (modulo a b) 0) (= (modulo b a) 0)))

  (define (dfs nums current visited count)
    (if (= (length current) (length nums))
        (set! count (modulo (+ count 1) mod-val))
        (for ([i (length nums)])
             (when (and (not (vector-ref visited i))
                        (or (null? current)
                            (can-place? (list-ref nums i) (car current))))
               (vector-set! visited i #t)
               (dfs nums (cons (list-ref nums i) current) visited count)
               (vector-set! visited i #f))))
    count)

  (define (calculate-special-perms nums)
    (let ([visited (make-vector (length nums) #f)])
      (dfs nums '() visited 0)))

  (calculate-special-perms nums))
